                            "id": "MDk6TWlsZXN0b25lMTEwMTQyNw==",
                            "title": "Release New Curriculum",
                            "description": "We will be interlocking ourselves a lot more to Github as we have involved ourselves with Gitter so thoroughly.\r\n\r\nWe will also be moving from Express.js to Loopback.js(which runs on top of Express). At the same time we will also be using NGINX in production.\r\n\r\nThis move involves:\r\n\r\n* moving to loopback(done)\r\n* Add NGINX into production stack(done)\r\n* Migrating users to new db format(script ready)\r\n* Fixing various challenge bugs.\r\n* Finishing up jQuery Curriculum.\r\n* Finalize JavaScript Curriculum.\r\n* Github auth locking\r\n* Launching Camperbot!(almost done)\r\n* Launching Hikes! Our new (OTG) on-the-go curriculum (almost done!)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
